itemDescription: Master Chief Petty Officer of the United States Navy, 1992-1998

wikipedia_page.main: John Hagan (born 20 May 1946) is a retired senior sailor of the United States Navy who served as the eighth Master Chief Petty Officer of the Navy.

response: * John Hagan, 8th master chief petty officer, US Navy
Revised Lyrics of 1997 by MCPON John Hagan, USN (Ret) which is used today by the Navy:
*John Hagan (sailor) (born 1946), eighth Master Chief Petty Officer of the Navy,
* John Hagan (Ohio politician), former Republican member of the Ohio House of Representatives
